data.description: Welcome home... This home has undergone a comprehensive renovation, with every corner reflecting the effort and attention to detail. The bathrooms and kitchen, complete with sleek stainless steel appliances, have all been tastefully updated. Revel in the contemporary tile work throughout the house. Step outside to discover a picturesque pool area, complemented by a sheltered terrace, perfect for both relaxation and entertainment. This corner unit enjoys enchanting landscaping, providing an inviting ambiance. Additionally, there's ample space on the property for your boat or RV. No HOA!!
